                <head>No. 626<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Foreign Ministers of the United States, France, the United Kingdom, and the
                    Soviet Union held a Four-Power Conference in Berlin beginning January 25 through
                    February 18. For extensive <pb facs="0309" n="1399" xml:id="pg_1399"/>
                    documentation on the Berlin Conference, including bilateral meetings between
                    French and United States officials, see <ref target="frus1952-54v07p1#pg_601"
                        >volume VII, Part 1, pages 601</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
